@startuml
title 连铸过程控制系统（CCS）总体组件图 - 概要设计
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #EEF2F6
  BorderColor #7B7B7B
  FontSize 12
}
left to right direction
' ======================
' 外部系统边界
' ======================
actor "操作员 (Operator)" as operator
actor "MES系统" as MES
node "PLC / Level1" as L1
' ======================
' CCS 系统边界
' ======================
node "连铸过程控制系统 (CCS)" as ccs {
  
  [计划调度模块\nScheduling & Planning] as Planning
  [执行控制模块\nExecution Control] as Execution
  [过程控制模块\nProcess Control] as Process
  [通信模块\nCommunication Interface] as Comm
  [数据服务模块\nData Service] as Data
  [操作与监控界面\nHMI / Operator Console] as HMI
}
' ======================
' 外部交互
' ======================
MES --> Comm : 板坯计划\n炉次计划下发
Comm --> MES : 状态反馈 / 实绩数据
operator --> HMI : 操作指令 / 监控信息
HMI --> Execution : 作业启动 / 状态查询
L1 <--> Process : 实时信号采集 / 控制指令
' ======================
' 内部模块交互
' ======================
Comm --> Planning : 传递计划数据
Planning --> Execution : 生成作业指令
Execution --> Process : 下发工艺控制目标
Process --> Data : 采样 / 实时数据上报
Data --> Execution : 提供实时信息支撑
Data --> HMI : 提供显示 / 报表数据
@enduml
